snippet.title: How To Make Money With Code!
snippet.description:
How To Make Money With Code

These are my best tips for how to make money from code. There are tons of way to make money with code, but these are my best recommendations.

Download Kite here: https://kite.com/download/?utm_medium=referral&utm_source=youtube&utm_campaign=kallehallden&utm_content=make-money-with-code
It is by far my favourite plugin for vs code, awesome productivity tool for developers!
